rows.label: tlk41700121_06_msg0001
rows.name:
About a decade ago, the leadership of
a town ruled by one of Gula's seven
main clans changed hands.

rows.label: tlk41700121_06_msg0002
rows.name:
The old leader had two daughters,
but one of them was really sickly.

rows.label: tlk41700121_06_msg0003
rows.name:
He was spending crazy amounts of
money on medical care for her.

rows.label: tlk41700121_06_msg0004
rows.name:
Including money from his
people's taxes.

rows.label: tlk41700121_06_msg0005
rows.name:
It's not like I can't empathize.
Any father would want to do whatever
he could to save his precious daughter.

rows.label: tlk41700121_06_msg0006
rows.name:
But when you're leader of a whole clan,
a whole town...you have responsibilities.

rows.label: tlk41700121_06_msg0007
rows.name:
Not like Consul Morph was any
better, mind. I hope we get a half-
decent consul next time...
